              <div>
                <div class="czx-step__h">Hard Water Enters</div>
                <div class="czx-step__p">Water containing calcium and magnesium reaches the Corzin unit.</div>
                <div class="czx-pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Works with Borewell & Tanker Water</div>
              </div>
            </button>

            <button class="czx-step" type="button" data-czx-step="2" data-czx-img="https://corzingroup.com//wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Base_style_append__Photorealistic_comm-11.jpg">
              <div class="czx-step__num">2</div>
              <div>
                <div class="czx-step__h">Neutralization Process</div>
                <div class="czx-step__p">Food-grade media reduces mineral bonding so scale doesn’t stick to surfaces.</div>
                <div class="czx-pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> No Salt Refilling Needed</div>
              </div>
            </button>

            <button class="czx-step" type="button" data-czx-step="3" data-czx-img="https://corzingroup.com//wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Base_style_append__Photorealistic_comm-12.jpg">
              <div class="czx-step__num">3</div>
              <div>
                <div class="czx-step__h">Conditioned Water Flows</div>
                <div class="czx-step__p">Water flows through your home with dramatically reduced scaling and buildup.</div>
                <div class="czx-pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Protects Pipes & Appliances</div>
              </div>
            </button>
          </div>

